<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q22_v5" title="Q22_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      La diagonal de un prisma recto de base rectangular se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:msqrt>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msup><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:msup><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:msqrt>
      </m:math>,
      con a, b y c las medidas de sus aristas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Un cable recorre el interior de una caja con forma de prisma recto de base rectangular desde una esquina inferior frontal hasta la esquina superior posterior y luego continúa 
      <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> cm fuera de la caja en un tramo recto adicional. 
      La longitud total del cable es de 
      <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math> cm, y dos de las aristas de la caja miden 
      <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> cm y 
      <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> cm.
      ¿Cuánto mide la tercera arista de la caja?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">4 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si la tercera arista midiera <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> cm, la diagonal interior sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>61</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que no es <m:math><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:math> cm. Como el cable total mide <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math> cm y <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> cm están fuera de la caja, la parte interior debe medir exactamente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">2 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La parte interior del cable mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>49</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. De ahí se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y, por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">6 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si la tercera arista midiera <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> cm, la diagonal interior sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>81</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm. Al sumar los <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> cm fuera de la caja, el cable mediría <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm, no <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math> cm.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">9 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si la tercera arista midiera <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cm, la diagonal interior sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>126</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que es mayor que <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math> cm. Al sumar además los <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> cm fuera de la caja, la longitud total sería mayor que <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math> cm, así que no puede ser <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math> cm.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="FB_NoResponse" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p>Debes seleccionar una alternativa. Recuerda que la parte del cable dentro de la caja mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cm y corresponde a la diagonal interior del prisma.</p>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar la parte del cable que está dentro de la caja</strong></p>
            <p>La longitud total del cable es 11 cm, pero 4 cm están fuera de la caja.</p>
            <p>Entonces, la diagonal interior del prisma mide:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              cm
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Plantear la fórmula de la diagonal del prisma</strong></p>
            <p>Dos aristas miden 3 cm y 6 cm. Si la tercera arista es <m:math><m:mi>c</m:mi></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                      <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                      <m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                      <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                      <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Elevar al cuadrado ambos lados</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>36</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>49</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Despejar la tercera arista</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>49</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>49</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>c</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La tercera arista de la caja mide <strong>2 cm</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_NoResponse</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>